CORPORATIONS

The ramparts of the small independent businesses have fallen in the world of
Shadowrun, and huge dominating Corporations have taken the lead. Corporations
range from small non-competetive conglomerates to the forbearing forms of such
Megacorporations as Aztechnology and Renraku. The Corporations are Shadowrunners
staple source of business and employment, as the large faceless powers require
secretive individuals to carry out their dirty work.

^WSee Also: AZTECHNOLOGY, RENRAKU^n

